rest in peace to one of my musical mentors and friend, George Brown, one of the founding members of @koolandthegang

You have been a man of dignity, respect, integrity, and wisdom. I will continue to carry fond memories in my heart and will always be a fan. 

sending my deepest prayers to his family, colleagues, friends and fans around the world. 🕊️🙏🏽
